Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The battle between the Roger Pirates\Nand the Whitebeard Pirates lasted three days and three nights,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and turned into a banquet at the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the same time, Roger found out\Nthat Oden could read the script on the Road Ponegliff{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}which details the location \Nof the last island...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a year will do.\NLet me borrow Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Newgate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Are you trying to\Ntake my family member away from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,White-Kichi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Devoting His Life!\NRoger's Adventure!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gather up all of the crew!\NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sea wind blows to where, who knows?\NThe waves will be our guide!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O'er across the ocean's tide, \Nthe sunset is goin' wild{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See the sky! Birds singing \Nin circles passing by!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bid farewell to weaver's town!\NSay so long to port renowned!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sing a song, it won't be long \Nbefore we're casting off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cross the gold and silver waves, \Nchangin' into water sprays!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sailing out on our journey \Nto the ends of the sea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna travel like this forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as long as time allows...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Captain, did you catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} something, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only got a year to live at most!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm living life at top speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Log Pose is pointing at the sky...\NIs it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not... Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming... The Knock Up Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sky Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, all the way from the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--{\i1}Heso{\i0}!\N--{\i1}Heso{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world is big! There is \Nstill so much more to it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even Buddha couldn't imagine\Nthat there were people living in the sky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes at least 10 years to handle a waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the City of Gold, Shandora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hold our true motive in your hearts\Nand speak not of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the ones who weave history...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With the sounding of the grand belfry..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The grand belfry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where it was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be Shandora's grand belfry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pure gold!\NCaptain, how should we take it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you become a captain,\Ncome get it yourself, Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! At least a piece of it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This stone is easy to find\Nsince it has a strong voice inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's talking about a great power, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The writing is about a weapon named Poseidon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oden, you can also write the script, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then carve this message!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger is near the end of his life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:09.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is hard to believe, but if \Nhe is living with such urgency,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.05,Italics,,0,0,0,,I will accompany him all the way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm... It's perfect, Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"I made it here. I will guide\Nthis text to the ends of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Gol D. Roger."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must see it, Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The final chapter of the great adventure\Nthat you're devoting your life to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Let's go back to the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heso{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing is done,\Nwe'll be smashed against the waves and broken to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!\NSkypiea's famous Octo-Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,An octopus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's a balloon!\N--How interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The octopus is deflating!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,--That was scary-{\i1}meow{\i0}.\N--Was it an air leak?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to come down alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the help of Ganfor, the god above the clouds,\Nwe reached the sea safely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the North Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the South Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--The North Pole!\N--The South Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna keep it up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am! Because I'm right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys fight all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares which one is colder,\Nthe North Pole or the South Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really wanna know,\Ngo to both places and see yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool your heads, idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to both the North \NPole and the South Pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, where should we go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, our destination is\Nthe last island on the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But to get there,\Nwe need copies of all four Road Ponegliffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The stone that we found on the Sky Island?\NThere is one in the Land of Wano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Mokomo Dukedom has one, too-{\i1}meow{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those countries you guys are from\Nhave that stone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the one on the Sky Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's red though!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the one I wanted most!\NWhy didn't you tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll have two out of four!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've got a copy of Linlin's Road Ponegliff\Nwhich I took by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I know where \Nthe remaining one is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't believe it!\NWe'll really have all four!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to ruin the fun,\Nbut something is wrong with the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With my untrained eye,\NI can't tell what is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--Okay, I know where we should go.\N--Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Water Seven, the City of Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--The City of Water?\N--Sounds romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, we headed for the shipbuilding town\Nto repair the ship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:07.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,WATER SEVEN, CITY OF WATER, GRAND LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such massive water magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are fountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones they have here sure are gigantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The City of Water, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:23.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,TOM - SHIPWRIGHT WHO BUILT ROGER'S SHIP
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it here like, "boom"! Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tom-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you completed the train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the Sea Train?! No way!\NI'm still designing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what did you break?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You only come here\Nwhen your ship needed repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it fell from a high place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to the Sky Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Like, "boom"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But after that, boom!\NWe fell to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:13.97,On Top,,0,0,0,,KOKORO - A GOOD-LOOKING \NSECRETARY, TOM'S WORKERS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are as noisy as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanna hear all about your journey,\Nbut why don't you eat first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Some food is ready for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're working in your underwear,\Nwhat a high-spirited kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother me, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an orphan?!\NDo you want me to introduce you to our Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are pirates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, no!\NI was just abandoned by pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gather up all of the crew!\NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pirates we, we'll divide \Nand conquer all the seas!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the waves to rest our heads, \Nship beneath us as our bed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoisted high up on the mast \Nour Jolly Roger flies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somewhere in the endless sky, \Na storm has started comin' by!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waves are dancing having fun, \Nit's time to sound the drums!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:31.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,TEQUILA WOLF - A COUNTRY ON A BRIDGE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we let blow winds of fear, \Nthen the end of us is near!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even so, tomor-row the sun will rise again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:55.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,SABAODY ARCHIPELAGO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fish-Man Island, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been there with White-Kichi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drop your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you go,\Nyour chances of dying won't change!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will be born...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our ruler will be born.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh! Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NIt's the silent deep sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can hear it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Oden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's talking this deep in the water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki! That's the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting...\NIt seems like the whole island is in a bubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--The Fish-Man Tribe?!\N--They're all around us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, surface dwellers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on how you answer, \Nyou might be exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:10.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,NEPTUNE - KING OF THE RYUGU KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, wait, wait. Look closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! Roger! Great Knight Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! So you guys are gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not up to anything bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:35.96,On Top,,0,0,0,,MERMAID INLET, RYUGU KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, why are you scared of a prophecy?\NYou're better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The prophecy says someone will break\Nthe gate of the Fish-Man Island soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you guys are here\Nso most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune-{\i1}sama{\i0}, it's been broken!\NThe Sea Kings chewed up the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! The gentle Sea Kings did such a thing?!\NIt can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,--There is a hole in the outer bubble!\N--Patch it up! Give it a quick fix!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't prevent it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See?! It wasn't us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:16.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,SHARLEY - A PROPHET GIRL (THREE YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sea Kings are going crazy because\Nthey're waiting for the Mermaid Princess to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mermaid Princess?!\NThat's another prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the king will have a baby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! I'm not even married yet-{\i1}jamon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only enthroned a few months ago-{\i1}jamon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Neptune-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She even divined the day that \Nthe former king would die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that sexy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that hateful Mermaid Otohime's political demonstration\Nthe other day was predicted by her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Otohime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like it brought me any comfort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:20:01.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,FOREST OF THE SEA, RYUGU KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, the whole country is swayed\Nby that girl's prophecies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not here to listen to your personal story,\NNeptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,--How is it, Oden?\N--Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two,\Nso I thought we could get a lot of information,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but one of them isn't so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an apology letter \Nfrom someone named Joyboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! He \Nreally can read the script!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, by the way, do you have a weapon\Nto control the Sea Kings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sky Island's stone says it's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ancient Weapon that has a god's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Poseidon."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a slight chill\Nwhen I heard Sharley's prophecy earlier-{\i1}jamon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Once every few centuries in this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,a Mermaid who can talk \Nto the Sea Kings is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, that Mermaid is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So your daughter will become the weapon\Nthat will destroy the world someday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a prophecy-{\i1}jamon{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if it's called an Ancient Weapon,\Nit doesn't have to be used as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that Poseidon was a Mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sharley,\Nwhen will the Mermaid Princess be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,10!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's 10 years from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Roger, I can't believe you're interested in such a weapon!\NI'm disappointed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune, what we want is the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:22:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,vast amount of treasure that was left \Nby the people who called it a weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you relieved?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't come to kidnap your hairy daughter\Nwho'll be born someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be hairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gather up all of the crew!\NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could be today, could be \Ntomorrow. Twilight dreaming{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No longer can we now see, \Nshadow hands still waving free{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why worry, there's sure to \Nbe a moonlit night again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gather up all of the crew!\NTime to ship out Binks's Brew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sing a song, a lively song \Nfor all the oceans wide!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all is said and done, \Nwe all end up skeletons!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Endless, aimless, this story \Non the uproarious seas!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unprecedented! Unreachable!\NRoger nears his goal of traveling around the world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He bolsters up his body \Nwhich is wracked by disease{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and under the flag of the pledge,\Nhe takes control of his own fate and navigates the sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the farthest land of the Grand Line,\Nhe becomes the conqueror of the sea and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"The King of the Pirates is Born! \NArriving at the Last Island!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,